  <h1>Services</h1>

  <h2>Spiritual Direction</h2>
  <p>A quiet, prayerful space to listen for God’s movement in your life. Spiritual direction is not advice‑giving or problem‑solving — it is a slow, attentive practice of noticing where the Spirit is inviting you toward freedom, healing, and deeper belonging.</p>

  <h2>Pastoral Counseling</h2>
  <p>For those navigating emotional or spiritual challenges, pastoral counseling offers compassionate support rooted in presence and discernment. This space is especially helpful for seasons of grief, transition, identity questions, or spiritual disorientation.</p>

  <h2>Leadership Soul Care</h2>
  <p>For pastors, ministry leaders, and founders who carry the weight of responsibility. These sessions offer grounding, clarity, and a place to reconnect with your calling without pressure or performance.</p>

  <h2>Retreats & Guided Reflection</h2>
  <p>Half‑day or full‑day experiences designed for rest, listening, and renewal. Retreats include silence, guided reflection, prayer practices, and space to reconnect with what matters most.</p>

  <p>If you’re unsure which offering fits your season, we can explore that together in a conversation.</p>
